7
00:00:17.251 --> 00:00:19.219 line:-1 align:center
We are so excited to talk about


8
00:00:19.253 --> 00:00:21.555 line:-1 align:center
how to design user interfaces


9
00:00:21.588 --> 00:00:24.057 line:-1 align:center
that are discoverable.


10
00:00:24.091 --> 00:00:26.793 line:-1 align:center
Your app has amazing features,


11
00:00:26,827 --> 00:00:29,363 line:-2
but people might not know the
