15
00:00:37.905 --> 00:00:40.174 line:-2 align:center
If your interface
is discoverable,


16
00:00:40.207 --> 00:00:43.310 line:-2 align:center
it means that people should
be able to look at a screen


17
00:00:43,343 --> 00:00:45,345 line:-1
and, before they touch anything,


18
00:00:45.379 --> 00:00:49.149 line:-1 align:center
know what they can do, and how.


19
00:00:49.183 --> 00:00:50.517 line:-1 align:center
Let's use an example


20
00:00:50,551 --> 00:00:52,252 line:-1
